<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTPA9">
<l>uṭuttuk kaḷaintaniṉ pītaka vāṭai yuṭuttuk kalantatuṇṭu</l>
<l>toṭutta tuḻāymalar cūṭik kaḷaintaṉa cūṭumit toṇṭarkaḷōm</l>
<l>viṭutta ticaikkaru mamtirut tittiru vōṇat tiruviḻavil</l>
<l>paṭuttapain nākaṇaip paḷḷikoṇ ṭāṉukkup pallāṇṭu kūṟutumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We, [Your] servants, wear the yellow clothing that you wore and removed,</l>
<l>[we] eat that which was absorbed,</l>
<l>[we] wear the string of tulsi flowers that were worn and removed.</l>
<l>Correcting the karma of the region(s) that was released,</l>
<l>we proclaim “many years” to the one who slept</l>
<l>[upon] the recumbent hooded serpent during the holy festival of Tiruvōṇam.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
